#main-headline
  %h1
    The Maker's Deck


- images = ["card-fan", "the-cards", "many-packs"]

.chunk
  .visual
    = link_to '/content/images/'+images[0]+'-medium.jpg', :class => 'fancybox' do
      = image_tag '/assets/media/16-9.png',  :class => images[0]
  .text
    %h2 What is this?
    %p
      The Maker's Deck is a set of collectible trading cards.
    %p
      I love trading cards, but am neither interested in sports or fantasy games. So made the cards I would want to buy.

.chunk
  .visual
    = link_to '/content/images/'+images[1]+'-medium.jpg', :class => 'fancybox' do
      = image_tag '/assets/media/16-9.png',  :class => images[1]
  .text
    %h2 Can I get some?
    %p
      They will soon available Etsy. I am also preparing a Kickstarter-campaign. Get notice when whose things happen:
      %br
      %br
      = link_to 'Follow us on twitter', 'http://twitter.com/makersdeck', :class => 'button big'
      %br
      or 
      %br
      = link_to 'Join the mailing list', 'http://eepurl.com/pMUR5', :class => 'button big'

    / %p.mobilebuttons
    /   = link_to 'Mailing list', 'http://eepurl.com/pMUR5', :class => 'button big'
    /   = link_to 'Twitter', 'http://twitter.com/makersdeck', :class => 'button big'

.chunk
  .visual
    = link_to '/content/images/'+images[2]+'-medium.jpg', :class => 'fancybox' do
      = image_tag '/assets/media/16-9.png',  :class => images[2]
  .text
    %h2 Will this be open source?
    %p
      Yes. Besides releasing all files and artwork I will also share the process of how to make cards yourself.
    %p
      The plan is also to build a webapp to generate cards, make printable sheets and find other people in real life to trade cards with.
    %p
      Cheers,
      %br
      %a filtercake (fabian at makersdeck.com)


